overview: Highlights from the 1994-95 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry. ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 7 - the best selling sports tape in the world - and why wouldn't it be? We go over 400 games to get the best goals, saves, hits, bloopers, the odd tussle, and naturally COACHES CORNER highlights. Last year we featured safety tips - this year in ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 7 we feature 'How to buy hockey equipment that fits properly', a must for younger players. ROCK' EM SOCK' EM 7, the very best.
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 7
